body.name: Club Car DS "STAPLE ON" Golf Cart Seat Cover (Solid Color)

byLineInfo.name: Visit the Up To Par Covers Store

features: MADE IN U.S.A - All our products are proudly made in U.S.A and are made with high quality marine grade vinyl and top stitched for extra strength and to help prevent water from getting through. All our products are made to order. We politely ask for up to 5 business days to produce and ship.
Free samples of our colors are available by request. Just let us know what colors you would like to see. The colors on your screen may differ from what you actually receive.

This seat cover is designed specifically for the model cart listed in the title and in the pictures of this listing. They are designed to fit the original unaltered seating. If your cart does not match the title or pictures, it will not fit your seating. If you do not see your cart here, we have plenty of other options in our store. Click on our logo to see more options. You may also contact us and send pictures of your cart to help verify what you may need.

DIY - Easy to Install - This is a full replacement seat cover. They are designed to be stapled on. There will be enough material to wrap under the seat and staple. Mostly all pictures you see of our products are all customer done and a lot of our customers have zero to very little experience in upholstery work.
When your cart is complete. Please help us by reviewing the product. Send us pictures of your work. We love to see our products on your cart.
body.description: What's Included - Vinyl staple-on seat cover for seat and backrest.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars As close to "PERFECT" as it gets
reviews.reviewText: I cannot explain in words how happy I am with this cover set!!for the price, i honestly was not expecting much, HOWEVER, I was WRONG to "assume"!!!it fits PERFECTLY!! The company was even wise enough/kind enough to provide more then enough, extra material so it"ll fit the seat no matter the size of the foam inside. I was So impressed with the outcome, that i bought another set for my other cart, and will continue to do so with all my carts in the future.i would DEFINITELY recommend this product to anyone looking to replace their old, torn, worn out golf cart cushions!!!! 5 Star product FOR SURE!!!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 21, 2021
reviews.reviewText: I installed myself-took 2 hours. Very happy with result. Highest quality vinyl. Will last many years. My wife said it was a great deal. She is a seamstress and said it would have cost more to buy this quality vinyl and make a pattern. It’s a little work getting the cushions off from the cart, but I’m not a genius and got the job done without too much swearing. For the work required and expense of the product, I would do it again. Thanks!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 12, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Good communication with the seller as they inquired about our existing golf cart model. We sent several pictures and a dimensioned sketch. The resulting product was spot on with only slight tugging and pulling for proper fitment. We decided to leave the old vinyl covers in place to better secure the foam. Gently heating the new covers with a heat gun helps immensely; that, and a good staple gun!
